title: Dividends and Personal Interest Income for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1929-1946 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1966. Data Are Monthly Totals At Annual Rates. Source: Survey Of Current Business, August 1965 For 1946-1962 Data; July 1966 And Following Monthly Issues For 1963-1966 Data.

This NBER data series m08279b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
